    "The above offers some telling examples of anthropomorphism in AI but does not and indeed cannot provide an exhaustive account of this phenomenon or its connection to hype.",
    "Nevertheless, it seems fair to conclude that anthropomorphism is part of the hype surrounding AI systems because of its role in exaggerating and misrepresenting AI capabilities and performance.",
    "Furthermore, such over-inflation and misrepresentation is nothing mysterious.",
    "It is simply due to projecting human characteristics onto systems that do not possess them.",
    "Anthropomorphism and moral judgments about AIThe previous section showed the prevalence of anthropomorphism as exhibited across the field by researchers, developers, science communicators, and the public."
